## Overview

OKF + Forge lifecycle project scaffold. **OKF** (`.okf/`) is curated memory. **Forge MCP** servers handle lifecycle planning and signed packets. **OKF dispatch** (`scripts/okf-dispatch`) is the implementation delivery spine. **ForgeRelay** supports cross-tool continuity alongside OKF handoffs.

