## Quick start

```bash
make validate-launch   # scaffold validation
scripts/okf-validate   # OKF bundle validation
scripts/okf-dispatch status
scripts/forge-clone-siblings.sh   # optional — clone nicksinx/*Forge peers
cp .cursor/mcp-forge-lifecycle.json.example .cursor/mcp.json   # if not auto-written
```

After cloning Forge siblings, build each repo (`npm ci && npm run build`) and reload Cursor MCP.

Sync OKF skills from the bootstrap kit when needed:

```bash
scripts/okf-sync-skills --dry-run
scripts/okf-sync-skills
```

