## Layout

- `.okf/` — curated project context (promotion target for Forge artifacts)
- `.okf/forge/` — gitignored Forge workspaces (runtime state)
- `scripts/*-mcp.sh` — Forge MCP launchers (sibling repo layout)
- `scripts/okf-dispatch` — multi-role delivery pipeline
- `backlog/` — optional human task tracker (dispatch is canonical for agents)
- `docs/` — five-service setup guides and operator docs

